336
00:39:56.109 --> 00:40:19.529
Incoming livestream: And you also need to think about the approximate knowledge of many things present in AI. Like, it's not just the fact that it can analyze this data, but it's the fact that so much knowledge is encoded that you can start doing different pattern matching, right? So, it knows what, companies or domains are associated with government entities. And it was even familiar with things like the Fortune 100, or you could do the AI Top 15,


