00:40:34.719 --> 00:40:51.948
Incoming livestream: you know, Claude analyzing this data, anthropic models, other models, right, can identify that an encoded JWT is likely to contain claims that had signal worth extracting, right? Looking at an encoded string as an LLM and pulling out that sort of signal was surprising and creative, and something maybe I wouldn't have thought of.


