00:43:18.779 --> 00:43:37.418
Incoming livestream: And so, you know, 2.53, I just say, hey, go find all of the rules here that are trivial. Rules that have secrets, that have prefixes, it's a GET request or a POST request to validate the secret. It's really easy for an LLM to port that over. And, 30 minutes later, I have 58 new rules in a totally different engine.


356
00:43:37.419 --> 00:43:46.708
Incoming livestream: And it's less so about, like, what secret scanning tool you should be using, and it's very much about this idea that product content, rules,


