00:45:24.849 --> 00:45:42.479
Incoming livestream: then improves your ability on future scans to sort of repeat the cycle. And I think this is true outside of this, like, data analysis space. If you're building detections, right? If you're building, configuration rules, I think this same loop of using AI, but trying to use AI to get to determinism really applies.


